Note: Always perform the same operation on both sides to keep balance.

Systems of Linear Equations

Two or more linear equations solved together.

Methods:

Graphing – Plot both lines, intersection = solution.

Substitution – Solve one equation for a variable, substitute into the other.

Elimination – Add/subtract equations to eliminate one variable.

Example (Substitution):
Solve:

𝑦
