2.6 Solving Higher-Degree Equations

Steps:

Factor out GCF.

Look for special patterns (difference of squares, cubes, etc.).

Use Rational Root Theorem & synthetic division.

Factor resulting quadratic or cubic using standard methods.

Solve for all roots (real and complex).

